{"tid":1094342,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"周子瑜個樣依家變到好恐怖","createTime":"2019-04-06T08:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T23:45:06.000Z","uid":152123,"like":6,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"758e5c4d37667bb01f6e4d052158ed1fb624b092","tid":1094342,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T08:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fxMJPDd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfxMJPDd.jpg&h=35b652d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbea1b287aa570096ae3a8ce47fef8d22f0a88a3","tid":1094342,"uid":49918,"like":67,"dislike":3,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T08:49:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f170234e8abbea3230ef084d6d6abd551c6d066","tid":1094342,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T08:49:10.000Z","msg":"呢張相已經經過站姐ps"},{"pid":"8c275c2aaf6cd2a1c11be5ea87bd76ead776d427","tid":1094342,"uid":152123,"like":28,"dislike":6,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T08:50:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲粗嘢留番畀我，畀番條靚女你補血<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/Zj5B9Ea.png[img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZj5B9Ea.png%5Bimg%5D&d=174aH8n0e8hd5Ixdtq%2FhYhZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=80460072\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/Zj5B9Ea.png[img]</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MynwYx4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMynwYx4.jpg&h=871b2cb0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d3bafc251c14583ab9e7964529e7a2b0dfa2561","tid":1094342,"uid":74065,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T08:54:27.000Z","msg":"南韓女團TWICE的19歲台灣成員周子瑜，以甜美長相受到歌迷喜愛，美貌更成為南韓女生的整形範本。<span style=\"color: red;\">她的媽媽黃燕玲是台南知名醫美診所院長，被問到是否有人拿著子瑜的照片進廠維修，子瑜媽媽自豪的說：「她就是我生的啊，我就是美的範本！」更大方承認自已對醫美「已經中毒」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3486/d3486637.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3486%2Fd3486637.jpg&h=c2d36553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲周子瑜媽媽黃燕玲，以醫美診所院長身份出席活動。（圖／記者黃軍瑋攝）<br />\n<br />\n黃燕玲15日以醫美診所院長的身份，赴台北出席美容業大型活動，對於女兒周子瑜此次回台席程低調的說：「新聞都講得很清楚了，我再講的話人家覺得我炒新聞。」但講到醫美話匣子就關不上。她笑說：「我最喜歡客人問我醫美的問題，因為我臉上什麼都做過，你問哪一項我都有做過，知道什麼人適合什麼。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3486/d3486661.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3486%2Fd3486661.jpg&h=4e2b299b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜與媽媽黃燕玲合照有如姐妹。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">她大方承認自己從脈衝光、肉毒桿菌再打到玻尿酸，從額頭打到嘴唇，通通都嘗試過</span>，笑說：「打在嘴巴，有嘟嘟的感覺」。黃燕玲坦言：「有年紀了，必須要侵入式的美容，才會有效。」<br />\n<br />\n黃燕玲笑說自己前兩天才補打了玻尿酸，更鼓勵記者：「微整就是慢慢調，年輕就開始做，以後就不用動刀了。」從事醫美事業不免得親自體驗，但黃燕玲豪氣地說：<span style=\"color: red;\">「我經常覺得不夠滿意，因為我已經（對醫美）中毒了。」<br />\n</span><br />\n不過青春洋溢的子瑜保證是純天然，尤其招牌的「W溝下巴」更讓黃燕玲驕傲表示：「那是媽媽生得好。」也笑說：「到我診所不用拿子瑜的照片啦，問媽媽比較快！」聽到子瑜的下巴是不少女生的整形範本，黃燕玲也用專業口吻表示：「台灣的技術就做得很好了，不用去韓國！」"},{"pid":"1dfb6146f3b885e1bb5d2d66f35d16918182f5d0","tid":1094342,"uid":76098,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:54:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同佢隻狗愈黎愈似樣"},{"pid":"479f27daef17b8b100e4db4750a0e3356907a632","tid":1094342,"uid":167658,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b3xH5zw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb3xH5zw.png&h=fc2ce1bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"707824841ce6442d62399223b2ddf5f8dba5b6b1","tid":1094342,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"479f27daef17b8b100e4db4750a0e3356907a632","tid":1094342,"uid":167658,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b3xH5zw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb3xH5zw.png&h=fc2ce1bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:5